thread.title_full: TAXIBOX mobile self-storage reviewed by Jessica

author: Jessica
title: Jessica
text: I was very impressed with the service i received at all stages of our booking. From the initial enquiry, to the taxi box drop off, pick up and the return of our box again. Everyone i spoke to along the way offered a high level of customer service which made the process easy and effortless for me the customer.
